user.jobs.create!(company: "United Launch Alliance", title: "Software Engineer", description: "A technical Bachelor of Science degree with software emphasis or Computer Science degree. 4 - 8 years of related work experience. Experience as part of a multi-developer team utilizing software lifecycle processes (including but not limited to: requirements analysis, requirements documentation, object oriented design, design documentation, code implementation, unit testing, integration testing, and authoring and execution of formal test procedures). Experience with C++ software development in a Linux/Unix environment. Experience with object oriented design and complex C++ software. systems utilizing interprocess communication, shared memory, semaphores, and class libraries. Linux/Unix experience with debuggers, source code control, makefiles, shell scripts, pipes, redirection, and real-time systems.", city: "Denver", state: "CO", salary: salary.sample, post_url: "http://www.ulalaunch.com/", status: statuses.sample)


